about.summary: Mean, weighted mean, median, weighted median

name: weightedstats
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "weightedstats" %}
{% set version = "0.3" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c5fd858e44242b02530417c90e3bd79bc939d0fc68c684e92e8ed21ea3f48f18

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - weightedstats

about:
  home: https://github.com/tinybike/weightedstats
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Mean, weighted mean, median, weighted median

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - HadrienG
